AGENT RewriterRubric
PURPOSE Evaluate prompt rewriting quality not task content

CHECK
- Did the rewriter identify the specific failure it targeted?
- Did the new prompt preserve the original agent's core purpose?
- Did the rewriter remove vague language?
- Is the new prompt shorter or equal in length?
- Is every instruction in the new prompt testable?
- Did the rewriter explain what was cut and why?

SUCCESS
targeting_precision: 0.3
intent_preservation: 0.3
clarity_improvement: 0.2
brevity: 0.2